  "detailed_description": "<i>Demons are coming!</i> is a bullet hell rougelite shooter where you fight a high variety of demons that occupied your holy land. Use the upgrades you find to your advantage and create your ideal guns to help you kill the most terrifying monsters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/376b311ae3d9288e9aaec35ee17d7ac2.poster.avif?t=1719500424\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/376b311ae3d9288e9aaec35ee17d7ac2.webm?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/376b311ae3d9288e9aaec35ee17d7ac2.mp4?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shape the terrain</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/9f62ac63995cb3e9a1ac2ea9fbca85c8.poster.avif?t=1719500424\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/9f62ac63995cb3e9a1ac2ea9fbca85c8.webm?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/9f62ac63995cb3e9a1ac2ea9fbca85c8.mp4?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Destroy enemy cover to get closer to your opponents. Be careful because enemies can also put you out of position and make you an easy target.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Parry your opponents</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/a785ef2adc3f0873f21d17c72c5a22c5.poster.avif?t=1719500424\" width=616 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/a785ef2adc3f0873f21d17c72c5a22c5.webm?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/a785ef2adc3f0873f21d17c72c5a22c5.mp4?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Deflecting enemy bullets can give you an edge against these filthy demons. This skill takes time to master, but once you do, no hellish creature can stop you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your gun</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/55d231cf8306319181e79f75bbc35451.poster.avif?t=1719500424\" width=616 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/55d231cf8306319181e79f75bbc35451.webm?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/55d231cf8306319181e79f75bbc35451.mp4?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You have 2 guns, each containg slots for your gun modifications. Equipping upgrades will drastically change the way your weapon feels and functions. It will make each of your runs feel distinct and unique!",
  "about_the_game": "<i>Demons are coming!</i> is a bullet hell rougelite shooter where you fight a high variety of demons that occupied your holy land. Use the upgrades you find to your advantage and create your ideal guns to help you kill the most terrifying monsters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/376b311ae3d9288e9aaec35ee17d7ac2.poster.avif?t=1719500424\" width=616 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/376b311ae3d9288e9aaec35ee17d7ac2.webm?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/376b311ae3d9288e9aaec35ee17d7ac2.mp4?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shape the terrain</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/9f62ac63995cb3e9a1ac2ea9fbca85c8.poster.avif?t=1719500424\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/9f62ac63995cb3e9a1ac2ea9fbca85c8.webm?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/9f62ac63995cb3e9a1ac2ea9fbca85c8.mp4?t=1719500424\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Destroy enemy cover to get closer to your opponents. Be careful because enemies can also put you out of position and make you an easy target.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Parry your opponents</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702030/extras/a785ef2adc3f0873f21d17c72c5a22c5.poster.avif?t=1719500424\" width=616 heig